  "summary": {
    "title": "Summary",
    "columns": 1,
    "hidden": false,
    "content": "<p>Full-stack developer who has spent 3+ years turning complex problems into clean, scalable solutions. From building enterprise analytics platforms with <strong>React</strong> and <strong>Next.js</strong> to architecting <strong>microservices</strong> with <strong>NestJS</strong>, <strong>Rust</strong>, and <strong>Golang</strong> - I bring end-to-end ownership to everything I ship. Proven track record of owning large-scale revamps, delivering embeddable API-driven products, and working with <strong>gRPC</strong>, <strong>GraphQL</strong>, <strong>REST</strong>, <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>, and <strong>Docker</strong>. At my best in startups where speed and craftsmanship both matter.</p>"
  },
