          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Orchestrated the <strong>full product and website revamp</strong>, delivering a modernized experience across search, insights, data model, and semantic table interfaces.</p></li><li><p>Boosted <strong>website performance and SEO</strong> by implementing lazy image loading, schema markup, accessibility improvements, and resource page optimizations.</p></li><li><p>Drove <strong>end-to-end feature delivery</strong> across the product - from natural language search and data model enhancements to query validation - enabling enterprise users to extract insights from their databases effortlessly.</p></li><li><p>Shipped <strong>data visualization and analytics UI</strong> including bar graphs, chart filters, and metric tabs, empowering knowledge workers to query and analyze enterprise databases through natural language.</p></li><li><p>Built and launched an <strong>embeddable search portal</strong>, enabling customers to integrate Tursio's AI-powered search directly into their own websites via a simple script tag.</p></li></ul><p></p>",
          "roles": []
        },
        {
