          "location": "Bangalore, India",
          "period": "September 2023 - May 2025",
          "website": {
            "url": "https://gida.in/",
            "label": ""
          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Shipped full-stack web applications for <strong>Max Group</strong> and <strong>HDFC</strong> using <strong>Next.js</strong> and <strong>NestJS</strong>, delivering robust and scalable products used by thousands of enterprise users.</p></li><li><p>Engineered and integrated <strong>RESTful APIs</strong> powering efficient data management, user authentication, and core business workflows across multiple client platforms.</p></li><li><p>Leveraged <strong>Next.js SSR and SSG</strong> to significantly improve application performance, page load times, and SEO across all products.</p></li><li><p>Took end-to-end ownership of multiple products - <strong>AgeEasyByAntara</strong>, <strong>Ergo Self-Help Portal</strong>, and <strong>Convenex Portal</strong> - from development through production deployment.</p></li></ul>",
          "roles": []
        },
