            "label": ""
          },
          "description": "<ul><li><p>Architected a <strong>provider-agnostic payment system</strong> using an adapter pattern, decoupling the platform from any single payment provider and future-proofing the billing infrastructure.</p></li><li><p>Integrated <strong>Stripe</strong> with webhook support and 2-way verification, ensuring secure and reliable transaction validation end-to-end.</p></li><li><p>Built the <strong>PaymentMethod model</strong> enabling users to securely store payment methods and supporting recurring payments independent of the underlying provider.</p></li><li><p>Designed and shipped a seamless <strong>transaction flow</strong> powering the platform's core billing experience.</p></li></ul>",
          "roles": []
        },
        {
