          "description": "<ul><li><p>Engineered and enhanced multiple core product modules - <strong>Payment</strong>, <strong>Notification</strong>, <strong>Billing/Account</strong>, <strong>Wallet</strong>, <strong>Store</strong>, and <strong>Product</strong> - using <strong>GraphQL</strong>, <strong>TypeScript</strong>, and <strong>ArangoDB</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Designed a <strong>type-safe model architecture</strong> that strengthened security, eliminated potential vulnerabilities, and set a clean foundation for scalable feature development.</p></li><li><p>Delivered end-to-end feature work across a complex multi-module platform, contributing to a consistent and reliable user-facing product experience.</p></li></ul>",
